# {{lb|fr|military}} Military rank used in some Francophone countries and formerly France that corresponds to the French rank of [[major]]; [[senior warrant officer]], [[senior]] [[adjutant]], [[sergeant major]]
types.html:
adjudant-major m (plural adjudants-majors)

  1. (military) Military rank used in some Francophone countries and formerly France that corresponds to the French rank of major; senior warrant officer, senior adjutant, sergeant major
trans: Military rank used in some Francophone countries and formerly France that corresponds to the French rank of major
senior warrant officer, senior adjutant, sergeant major
